Hi HC Tang, Xavier Ong, Sabrina Chee, Murphy Yap, Vivian Lim, Brian Tan Tze Mian and Felix Chua, 

We're very sorry for this error on our part. There was a technical outage with our system over the weekend, thus you were unable to view your card balance nor were you able to enjoy your rewards. 

The true monetary value of your card is still intact. The issue has been fixed and the full functionality of the card account has been restored. 

Please accept our sincere apologies for this technical glitch. We have forwarded this to our IT department they are working on this to prevent such incident from happening again.  

If you’re still facing issues with your account, or if you were unable to enjoy your reward over the weekend, please do drop us a PM with your registered Starbucks email address and we’ll look into this on our end. 

Thank you and we’re terribly sorry about the inconvenience caused.
